WEBVTT

00:00:09.160 --> 00:00:09.720
What's the price?

00:00:10.599 --> 00:00:11.199
Buddy.

00:00:11.400 --> 00:00:13.039
Someone's offering two hundred now.

00:00:14.160 --> 00:00:15.039
Two hundred?

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:17.679
I'll go a bit higher. I'll take it.

00:00:19.239 --> 00:00:20.079
Sounds great.

00:00:21.480 --> 00:00:22.399
I might not have anything else,

00:00:22.559 --> 00:00:23.600
but I've got plenty of money.

00:00:24.719 --> 00:00:25.399
It's dark out.

00:00:25.600 --> 00:00:26.559
I'm afraid I'll get duped.

00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:27.640
Let me take another look.

00:00:32.840 --> 00:00:33.520
I was just wondering,

00:00:33.880 --> 00:00:34.880
buddy, why are you doing business

00:00:39.719 --> 00:00:40.880
in the middle of the night?

00:00:41.479 --> 00:00:42.280
I'm talking to you.

00:00:43.200 --> 00:00:44.479
Looking at a vase.

00:00:45.320 --> 00:00:45.960
What kind of vase?

00:00:50.280 --> 00:00:51.079
My vase!

00:00:51.079 --> 00:00:51.920
Stop! Stop!

00:00:51.920 --> 00:00:52.520
Stop!

00:00:52.520 --> 00:00:53.479
You can't leave!

00:00:53.479 --> 00:00:54.679
Stop! You can't leave!

00:00:56.640 --> 00:00:57.920
Chen Dahui!

00:01:00.520 --> 00:01:01.600
My vase!

00:01:02.240 --> 00:01:03.119
The vase!

00:01:06.280 --> 00:01:07.920
Chen Dahui!

00:01:08.719 --> 00:01:10.480
I'm not done with you!

00:01:31.079 --> 00:01:32.480
Did you get a clear look at the driver?

00:01:34.040 --> 00:01:34.760
I didn't notice.

00:01:34.760 --> 00:01:37.120
Just an ordinary middle-aged man.

00:01:40.079 --> 00:01:40.799
What about the license plate?

00:01:42.159 --> 00:01:43.519
It was really chaotic at the time.

00:01:43.680 --> 00:01:44.719
I only remember

00:01:45.239 --> 00:01:47.040
the last two digits seemed to be

00:01:47.040 --> 00:01:48.040
one and five.

00:01:50.599 --> 00:01:51.719
There's no surveillance around here.

00:01:51.920 --> 00:01:53.799
We can only check nearby traffic cameras.

00:01:54.319 --> 00:01:55.400
Look at this time frame,

00:01:55.400 --> 00:01:56.680
check all vehicles coming and going,

00:01:56.799 --> 00:01:58.000
and find the suspect's car.

00:01:59.719 --> 00:02:00.280
Captain Chu.

00:02:00.519 --> 00:02:02.280
I think this is just an accident.

00:02:02.680 --> 00:02:03.799
The driver was inexperienced,

00:02:04.040 --> 00:02:04.959
hit the gas instead of the brake,

00:02:04.959 --> 00:02:06.079
and accidentally hit someone.

00:02:06.200 --> 00:02:08.080
It shouldn't be a criminal case.

00:02:08.520 --> 00:02:09.319
This Yu Tianfang,

00:02:09.800 --> 00:02:11.080
always makes a big deal out of nothing.

00:02:14.400 --> 00:02:15.680
You're just afraid a case will

00:02:15.680 --> 00:02:17.120
affect the restaurant's business, right?

00:02:17.919 --> 00:02:19.199
You really are my own mother.

00:02:20.199 --> 00:02:21.120
Don't say that.

00:02:21.120 --> 00:02:22.800
Boss Bai cares about you too.

00:02:22.800 --> 00:02:23.639
If she cared about me,

00:02:23.639 --> 00:02:25.319
she wouldn't withhold my inheritance.

00:02:26.759 --> 00:02:27.360
Qibao!

00:02:30.199 --> 00:02:31.840
This kid has such a temper.

00:02:32.159 --> 00:02:33.479
I really can't control her,

00:02:33.879 --> 00:02:35.560
so I can only control her belongings.

00:02:35.879 --> 00:02:36.560
From now on,

00:02:36.840 --> 00:02:37.800
I won't bother anymore.

00:02:38.960 --> 00:02:39.639
Don't worry.

00:02:40.120 --> 00:02:42.280
She'll understand our intentions one day.

00:02:42.560 --> 00:02:43.560
I hope so.

00:02:44.919 --> 00:02:46.000
The restaurant opens tomorrow.

00:02:46.280 --> 00:02:47.400
You two should come and support us.

00:02:47.840 --> 00:02:48.280
Right.

00:02:48.520 --> 00:02:49.240
Everyone come support us.

00:02:51.280 --> 00:02:52.680
If there's nothing else, we'll head back now.

00:03:07.879 --> 00:03:09.199
My eyes are getting blurry.

00:03:09.560 --> 00:03:10.120
Captain Chu.

00:03:13.479 --> 00:03:14.840
Why didn't you give it to me?

00:03:14.840 --> 00:03:16.159
From now on, when you have good stuff,

00:03:16.479 --> 00:03:17.599
you have to share it with me.

00:03:18.319 --> 00:03:18.800
Found it.

00:03:21.120 --> 00:03:22.280
During the time of the incident,

00:03:23.199 --> 00:03:24.000
in the nearby area,

00:03:24.560 --> 00:03:25.759
silver vehicle, plate ending in 15.

00:03:26.039 --> 00:03:27.199
Grey suit, red tie.

00:03:27.520 --> 00:03:28.120
That's him.

00:03:29.319 --> 00:03:31.199
This face looks so familiar.

00:03:32.319 --> 00:03:33.319
Where have I seen him?

00:03:35.599 --> 00:03:36.960
Give me back my antique vase!

00:03:36.960 --> 00:03:38.599
It's the Guo family's most valuable item!

00:03:38.599 --> 00:03:39.439
I'm warning you,

00:03:39.599 --> 00:03:40.840
there's a limit to making a scene.

00:03:41.080 --> 00:03:41.479
Chu Feng.

00:03:41.719 --> 00:03:43.280
Who told you to go arrest him?

00:03:43.280 --> 00:03:43.680
Chu Feng.

00:03:43.680 --> 00:03:44.280
I don't care!

00:03:44.439 --> 00:03:45.560
You're going to pay for it today!

00:03:45.680 --> 00:03:47.199
I went to him for a collateral loan,

00:03:47.319 --> 00:03:48.599
and you just barged in and arrested him!

00:03:48.759 --> 00:03:49.759
He took my vase,

00:03:50.000 --> 00:03:50.919
smashed it, and ran!

00:03:51.080 --> 00:03:52.360
You have to pay for it!

00:03:52.360 --> 00:03:53.039
I'm warning you,

00:03:53.039 --> 00:03:54.199
move again and it's assaulting an officer.

00:03:54.639 --> 00:03:55.479
Stop it!

00:03:55.719 --> 00:03:56.599
Let go of my dad!

00:03:56.599 --> 00:03:58.199
I'll take you all on today!

00:03:59.520 --> 00:03:59.960
Don't move!

00:04:01.120 --> 00:04:02.919
Chu Feng, cuff him. Apprehend him.

00:04:03.039 --> 00:04:04.120
You hurry home.

00:04:04.120 --> 00:04:04.759
I'll handle things here.

00:04:04.759 --> 00:04:05.240
No.

00:04:05.560 --> 00:04:06.439
I'm going with you.

00:04:06.439 --> 00:04:08.319
Can't let people who twist the truth win.

00:04:08.439 --> 00:04:09.719
The police are beating people!

00:04:11.520 --> 00:04:12.680
All right, everyone break it up.

00:04:12.800 --> 00:04:13.560
Move along, move along.

00:04:13.759 --> 00:04:14.240
It's nothing.

00:04:22.519 --> 00:04:23.680
You went too hard on him back then.

00:04:24.360 --> 00:04:25.480
Guo Yi's arm was dislocated.

00:04:25.959 --> 00:04:26.959
And you got disciplined for it.

00:04:29.120 --> 00:04:29.560
Right.

00:04:30.480 --> 00:04:31.079
It's him.

00:04:31.319 --> 00:04:32.279
Haven't seen him in years.

00:04:32.279 --> 00:04:34.399
He's unhinged enough to run people over.

00:04:35.279 --> 00:04:36.800
He's probably mentally unstable too.

00:04:37.120 --> 00:04:38.079
The people he hates most...

00:04:38.399 --> 00:04:39.279
one is my dad,

00:04:39.720 --> 00:04:40.639
the other is Chen Dahui.

00:04:42.279 --> 00:04:44.079
But why would he hit He Siqi?

00:04:45.199 --> 00:04:46.680
Was it a random attack,

00:04:47.079 --> 00:04:48.639
or was He Siqi the target?

00:04:48.879 --> 00:04:50.680
We'll only know once we find him.

00:04:51.399 --> 00:04:53.079
I'll go look into Guo Yi right now.

00:04:59.759 --> 00:05:00.560
Tell me...

00:05:01.759 --> 00:05:02.639
that car...

00:05:02.839 --> 00:05:04.120
was it after me?

00:05:04.519 --> 00:05:06.000
You weren't the one who got hurt.

00:05:07.160 --> 00:05:07.920
If you ask me,

00:05:07.920 --> 00:05:09.920
the target was that pregnant woman.

00:05:09.920 --> 00:05:11.680
Maybe her husband owed money,

00:05:11.680 --> 00:05:12.279
and the debt collectors

00:05:12.560 --> 00:05:13.920
went after his wife.

00:05:13.920 --> 00:05:15.600
You think everyone's like you,

00:05:15.600 --> 00:05:17.040
running loans and chasing debts?

00:05:18.439 --> 00:05:19.839
We're a legitimate company.

00:05:20.040 --> 00:05:21.360
We only do pawn business.

00:05:21.360 --> 00:05:23.279
We never break the law.

00:05:23.920 --> 00:05:24.920
I don't believe you.

00:05:25.319 --> 00:05:26.439
You're definitely lying to me.

00:05:26.439 --> 00:05:27.519
Then let me ask you this.

00:05:27.720 --> 00:05:29.519
If someone needs help,

00:05:29.519 --> 00:05:31.120
and you lend them money,

00:05:31.319 --> 00:05:33.240
but they never pay you back,

00:05:33.399 --> 00:05:34.759
wouldn't you be furious?

00:05:35.079 --> 00:05:36.040
Of course I would.

00:05:36.040 --> 00:05:37.800
So shouldn't you teach them a little lesson?

00:05:37.800 --> 00:05:38.279
And then...

00:05:38.800 --> 00:05:39.759
give them a scare?

00:05:41.079 --> 00:05:42.639
Yeah, a scare's in order.

00:05:45.040 --> 00:05:46.000
Now you get it.

00:05:46.519 --> 00:05:47.120
Oh, right.

00:05:47.959 --> 00:05:48.800
Take my advice.

00:05:49.279 --> 00:05:50.680
Change careers while you still can.

00:05:50.959 --> 00:05:51.639
Otherwise,

00:05:52.160 --> 00:05:53.360
I'll always be worried about you.

00:05:53.800 --> 00:05:55.120
I want to change careers too.

00:05:55.519 --> 00:05:56.839
Who'd want this kind of job?

00:05:58.040 --> 00:05:59.160
But I have no choice.

00:05:59.439 --> 00:06:02.480
They'd rather be deadbeats than pay.

00:06:02.480 --> 00:06:04.879
The money I lend just turns into bad debt.

00:06:05.000 --> 00:06:05.879
It's not easy for me either.

00:06:08.480 --> 00:06:09.439
I know.

00:06:10.120 --> 00:06:11.800
You need a big sum of money right now

00:06:11.800 --> 00:06:12.879
to cover the deficit.

00:06:13.120 --> 00:06:13.879
But...

00:06:13.879 --> 00:06:15.800
that inheritance my real dad left me,

00:06:16.000 --> 00:06:16.720
that Bai woman

00:06:16.959 --> 00:06:18.240
just refuses to give it to me.

00:06:18.519 --> 00:06:20.439
If you won't even call her "Mom,"

00:06:20.439 --> 00:06:22.439
she'll never give you that money.

00:06:22.879 --> 00:06:23.759
That woman...

00:06:23.759 --> 00:06:25.839
she got to enjoy a passionate love affair.

00:06:26.120 --> 00:06:27.079
But me?

00:06:27.680 --> 00:06:29.879
I never knew what a family felt like.

00:06:31.199 --> 00:06:32.680
I know how hurt you feel.

00:06:33.040 --> 00:06:33.600
Qiqi,

00:06:33.839 --> 00:06:34.720
listen to me.

00:06:34.839 --> 00:06:36.399
The restaurant opens tomorrow.

00:06:36.399 --> 00:06:37.639
Go show your support.

00:06:37.639 --> 00:06:38.399
Play the dutiful daughter.

00:06:38.399 --> 00:06:40.120
You might just get that inheritance.

00:06:40.360 --> 00:06:41.000
Qiqi,

00:06:41.879 --> 00:06:42.680
you know

00:06:44.319 --> 00:06:45.839
I'm in real trouble right now.

00:06:46.319 --> 00:06:48.360
Only you can help me get through this.

00:06:49.439 --> 00:06:49.920
Well...

00:06:50.279 --> 00:06:51.480
it's getting late.

00:06:51.759 --> 00:06:52.480
I think

00:06:52.480 --> 00:06:53.319
I should head back.

00:06:53.759 --> 00:06:54.560
Stay safe.

00:06:56.600 --> 00:06:57.040
Hang in there.

00:06:58.839 --> 00:06:59.720
Be safe.

00:06:59.720 --> 00:07:00.319
Got it.

00:07:03.000 --> 00:07:03.680
Come on out.

00:07:08.360 --> 00:07:10.000
This is the most critical moment.

00:07:10.000 --> 00:07:11.199
Keep a close eye on her for me.

00:07:11.199 --> 00:07:12.040
Don't worry, Brother Hui.

00:07:36.600 --> 00:07:38.240
Is Bai Ruifen really broke?

00:07:39.920 --> 00:07:41.040
I don't buy it.

00:07:41.240 --> 00:07:42.959
She's pretending to be poor just for me.

00:07:52.399 --> 00:07:53.199
Boss Bai.

00:07:53.759 --> 00:07:54.959
Someone's outside looking for you.

00:07:55.279 --> 00:07:55.879
Boss Bai.

00:07:56.639 --> 00:07:57.759
Qibao.

00:07:59.040 --> 00:07:59.800
What are you doing here?

00:08:01.279 --> 00:08:02.360
Just pretend you didn't see anything.

00:08:03.160 --> 00:08:03.720
You...

00:08:05.920 --> 00:08:07.800
You're not here to steal the inheritance

00:08:08.639 --> 00:08:09.319
documents, are you?

00:08:09.720 --> 00:08:10.800
What do you mean, steal?

00:08:11.040 --> 00:08:12.600
That inheritance is mine to begin with.

00:08:15.720 --> 00:08:16.319
What?

00:08:16.519 --> 00:08:17.439
Why are you so desperate for money?

00:08:17.839 --> 00:08:18.319
How about

00:08:19.079 --> 00:08:19.920
I transfer you some first?

00:08:20.360 --> 00:08:21.000
What?

00:08:23.439 --> 00:08:24.319
You're gonna support me?

00:08:26.199 --> 00:08:27.240
Supporting you's fine,

00:08:27.879 --> 00:08:28.639
but

00:08:29.199 --> 00:08:30.839
let's not rush into it.

00:08:31.120 --> 00:08:32.200
The two of us...

00:08:32.360 --> 00:08:33.240
Are you out of your mind?

00:08:33.240 --> 00:08:33.639
We can take it slow...

00:08:33.639 --> 00:08:34.200
Get off!

00:08:35.600 --> 00:08:35.960
We can...

00:08:36.240 --> 00:08:37.080
take our time, you know?

00:08:39.039 --> 00:08:39.799
Qibao.

00:08:40.440 --> 00:08:40.960
Qibao.

00:08:41.159 --> 00:08:42.279
There are a lot of bad people out there.

00:08:42.279 --> 00:08:43.440
I can protect you if I tag along.

00:08:43.440 --> 00:08:44.519
Don't let anyone fool you.

00:08:44.519 --> 00:08:46.159
The one who can fool me hasn't been born.

00:08:46.159 --> 00:08:46.759
How about

00:08:46.919 --> 00:08:47.919
you try to fool me?

00:08:50.840 --> 00:08:51.279
Qibao.

00:08:51.480 --> 00:08:52.480
Scoot over a bit.

00:08:56.639 --> 00:08:58.559
I'm not even in yet, Qibao!

00:09:09.519 --> 00:09:10.080
Hey, driver.

00:09:10.279 --> 00:09:11.480
You didn't even ask where I'm going

00:09:11.480 --> 00:09:12.399
before you took off.

00:09:12.440 --> 00:09:14.919
At this hour, everyone's heading downtown.

00:09:18.039 --> 00:09:20.000
You look kind of familiar, you know?

00:09:20.000 --> 00:09:22.039
I've just got one of those common faces.

00:09:22.039 --> 00:09:24.080
Everyone thinks they know me.

00:09:24.320 --> 00:09:25.039
Hey, driver.

00:09:25.919 --> 00:09:27.440
How many years have you been driving?

00:09:27.440 --> 00:09:29.440
Your skills aren't all that great.

00:09:29.440 --> 00:09:30.879
I run a cold storage business.

00:09:30.879 --> 00:09:32.240
Business hasn't been great,

00:09:32.240 --> 00:09:33.120
so I drive on the side

00:09:33.600 --> 00:09:34.919
to make some pocket money.

00:09:36.440 --> 00:09:37.639
I think I've seen you before.

00:09:37.799 --> 00:09:38.480
Who are you?

00:09:41.840 --> 00:09:42.720
Let me out!

00:09:43.240 --> 00:09:44.000
I want out!

00:09:44.000 --> 00:09:44.840
Sit still!

00:10:47.200 --> 00:10:47.799
Old Chu.

00:10:47.799 --> 00:10:49.759
Qibao won't answer my calls.

00:10:50.080 --> 00:10:51.960
I've got a really bad feeling about this.

00:10:52.279 --> 00:10:55.480
My heart's all over the place right now,

00:10:55.600 --> 00:10:57.000
totally on edge.

00:10:57.480 --> 00:10:58.480
What's your relationship with her?

00:10:58.720 --> 00:11:00.039
Why should she have to answer your calls?

00:11:00.279 --> 00:11:01.000
Besides,

00:11:01.320 --> 00:11:01.919
are we really close enough that you...

00:11:05.440 --> 00:11:06.039
Chu Feng.

00:11:06.480 --> 00:11:07.600
Someone just jumped into the river here!

00:11:23.679 --> 00:11:24.679
One more step.

00:11:25.559 --> 00:11:26.039
I...

00:11:31.080 --> 00:11:32.240
What are you standing there for?

00:11:32.399 --> 00:11:33.080
Get up here, now!

00:11:33.639 --> 00:11:35.240
I was just calling you,

00:11:35.240 --> 00:11:36.480
when I heard a splash,

00:11:36.679 --> 00:11:38.600
and a lady jumped right in front of me.

00:11:39.080 --> 00:11:40.639
You're this old and have no common sense?

00:11:40.639 --> 00:11:41.200
Hey!

00:11:41.559 --> 00:11:42.000
Get up.

00:11:42.480 --> 00:11:43.480
Has the identity been confirmed?

00:11:44.240 --> 00:11:45.080
Okay, got it.

00:11:46.759 --> 00:11:48.279
The recovery team found her downstream.

00:11:48.440 --> 00:11:49.480
Confirmed to be Li Fang,

00:11:49.480 --> 00:11:50.879
the victim from the recent car accident.

00:11:52.480 --> 00:11:53.360
I remember.

00:11:53.360 --> 00:11:54.759
Her husband's name is Cao Li.

00:11:55.080 --> 00:11:56.120
Contact her husband first.

00:11:56.840 --> 00:11:57.639
Li Fang.

00:11:57.919 --> 00:11:59.039
Where is she now?

00:11:59.039 --> 00:11:59.639
Did you find her?

00:12:00.440 --> 00:12:02.440
She's on her way to the hospital.

00:12:03.039 --> 00:12:04.440
Looks like Old Li was right.

00:12:05.639 --> 00:12:06.960
I really am a jinx.

00:12:07.759 --> 00:12:08.840
You're pretty superstitious.

00:12:10.679 --> 00:12:11.600
Life is unpredictable.

00:12:11.840 --> 00:12:13.080
No one can prevent accidents.

00:12:13.600 --> 00:12:14.200
No answer.

00:12:14.759 --> 00:12:16.360
Qibao still hasn't picked up my calls.

00:12:16.360 --> 00:12:17.399
I'm still worried about her.

00:12:17.559 --> 00:12:18.279
I'm going to go find her.

00:12:23.039 --> 00:12:24.840
So much has happened in just one day.

00:12:25.279 --> 00:12:26.120
I'm worried that

00:12:26.120 --> 00:12:27.720
Cao Li can't handle such a huge blow.

00:12:27.879 --> 00:12:29.519
Notifying the family is always tough.

00:12:30.039 --> 00:12:31.480
Make sure to comfort him.

00:12:35.120 --> 00:12:36.320
What's going on with He Siqi?

00:12:38.039 --> 00:12:39.039
Not clear yet.

00:12:40.399 --> 00:12:41.240
Keep a close eye on it.

00:12:59.799 --> 00:13:00.480
You're awake.

00:13:01.240 --> 00:13:02.240
Let me make this clear.

00:13:02.840 --> 00:13:03.600
Don't even think about escaping.

00:13:03.600 --> 00:13:05.039
I tied a pig-tie knot.

00:13:05.279 --> 00:13:05.879
You,

00:13:05.879 --> 00:13:06.679
can't get away.

00:13:08.159 --> 00:13:09.159
Who... who are you?

00:13:09.399 --> 00:13:10.480
Are you kidnapping me?

00:13:11.639 --> 00:13:13.039
Don't make it sound so ugly.

00:13:13.960 --> 00:13:15.360
I'm just using you to settle a debt.

00:13:18.159 --> 00:13:19.480
My mom owes you money?

00:13:19.480 --> 00:13:20.279
Then go find her.

00:13:20.279 --> 00:13:21.679
Why are you tying me up?

00:13:24.440 --> 00:13:25.159
Let me ask you,

00:13:25.759 --> 00:13:27.399
is Chen Dahui your boyfriend?

00:13:29.080 --> 00:13:30.039
No, no.

00:13:30.039 --> 00:13:31.399
My boyfriend's name is Chen Hui.

00:13:31.960 --> 00:13:33.080
Did you make a mistake?

00:13:34.000 --> 00:13:34.600
No mistake.

00:13:34.759 --> 00:13:35.360
It's him.

00:13:35.799 --> 00:13:37.080
I'd recognize him even as ashes.

00:13:37.679 --> 00:13:38.480
He changed his name.

00:13:39.840 --> 00:13:41.240
He owes me money and won't pay.

00:13:42.080 --> 00:13:43.320
Changed his name and ran.

00:13:45.879 --> 00:13:47.360
That damn scammer.

00:13:49.080 --> 00:13:50.600
He owes you money?

00:13:51.440 --> 00:13:52.639
He doesn't seem the type.

00:13:54.799 --> 00:13:55.919
What do you mean, not the type?

00:13:57.480 --> 00:13:58.200
Back then,

00:13:58.879 --> 00:14:01.159
I took my family's heirloom antique vase

00:14:01.399 --> 00:14:03.279
to Chen Dahui for a collateral loan.

00:14:03.679 --> 00:14:05.120
Who knew he'd killed someone?

00:14:05.399 --> 00:14:06.679
The cops came to arrest him,

00:14:07.360 --> 00:14:09.200
he smashed my antique vase,

00:14:09.480 --> 00:14:10.720
and then ran off.

00:14:11.039 --> 00:14:11.759
He killed someone?

00:14:11.759 --> 00:14:13.279
Impossible. He couldn't kill anyone.

00:14:13.279 --> 00:14:14.399
Why not?

00:14:16.039 --> 00:14:17.120
Young girls like you

00:14:17.759 --> 00:14:19.480
are easily fooled by older men.

00:14:23.039 --> 00:14:25.039
Let me tell you something else you don't know.

00:14:25.279 --> 00:14:26.960
He not only killed someone who owed him,

00:14:27.279 --> 00:14:29.559
he also killed a cop who was chasing him.

00:14:29.559 --> 00:14:31.120
He's been on the run for years.

00:14:31.799 --> 00:14:33.480
I thought I'd never find him.

00:14:35.759 --> 00:14:37.279
Thank heavens!

00:14:37.679 --> 00:14:38.639
I was able to

00:14:39.159 --> 00:14:40.080
run into him on the street.

00:14:41.000 --> 00:14:41.799
Now I

00:14:42.679 --> 00:14:44.360
can finally get my revenge.